        "exhibit_introduce" : "Seoullo Media Canvas is a media art platform that expands the scope of media art by continuously displaying artworks made of electronic light, such as media art and video content that citizens can enjoy and sympathize with.",
        // "exhibit_introduce_sub" : "",
